<Base
  title="Research"
  description="Alpha Factory Research archive — evidence-based systematic trading research. Reality Check reports, forward evidence studies, and postmortem analyses."
>
  <h1>Research</h1>
  <p>Evidence-based reports on systematic trading strategies. Each report includes mechanism discovery, frozen backtesting, forward evidence collection, and cost/concentration analysis.</p>

  <h2>Founding Report</h2>
  <p style="color:var(--color-muted);font-style:italic;">Coming Soon — Join the waitlist</p>
  <p>The inaugural report covers which public crypto trading strategies survived our independent validation pipeline — and why the majority failed. Includes: liquidation cascade continuation, stop-hunt reversal, cross-venue funding dispersion, volatility compression, and pre-market convergence.</p>
  <a href="/" style="display:inline-block;padding:0.5rem 1.2rem;background:var(--color-text);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;font-size:0.9375rem;">Get Free Report</a>

  <hr />

  <h2>Reality Check</h2>
  <p>Structured falsification reports: mechanisms tested, gates passed, and postmortem analyses. Each Reality Check entry records the exact hypothesis, preregistered validation, and why it survived or was killed.</p>
  <p style="color:var(--color-muted);font-style:italic;">First reports publishing soon.</p>

  <hr />

  <h2>Methodology</h2>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Mechanism Discovery</strong> — identify structural market edges from public research, exchange data, and practitioner literature.</li>
    <li><strong>Data Feasibility Gate</strong> — verify obtainable, clean historical data before any engineering.</li>
    <li><strong>Reality Check</strong> — test causal chain and economic viability with frozen, preregistered backtests.</li>
    <li><strong>Forward Evidence</strong> — prospective paper trading before capital. No backtest-alone claims.</li>
    <li><strong>Cost & Concentration Audit</strong> — fees, slippage, funding, and single-trade dominance analysis.</li>
  </ol>
</Base>
